<template>
  <label>{{ label }}</label>
  <input
    v-bind:value="value"
    v-on:input="$emit('input', $event.target.value)"
    type="text"
  />
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "MisaInput",
  props: ["value"],
  methods: {},

  data() {
    return {};
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
